<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٨٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">سئل رسول اللَّه <span class="special">ﷺ</span> شيئا قط فقال:</span> لا <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
